00:41:17.930 --> 00:41:19.910
That's why we say something
is quintessential.

00:41:19.910 --> 00:41:22.720
It's heavenly, it's et cetera.

00:41:22.720 --> 00:41:24.420
So these are the
four essences.

00:41:24.420 --> 00:41:24.740
All right?

